OL,3,CParents pay tribute to 'perfect,
OL,4,Ccaring son' who died in crash
OL,6,FThe family of a man who died following
OL,7,Fa collision in Sussex have described
OL,8,Fhim as "loving, caring, fun and happy".
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to
OL,11,FJurys Gap Road, Camber, on Wednesday 4
OL,12,FFebruary, following a serious
OL,13,Fcollision at around 4.50am.
OL,15,FBen Richards, who was 27 and from St
OL,16,FLeonards was declared deceased at the
OL,17,Fscene.
OL,19,FIn a tribute to Ben, his parents said:
OL,20,F"He was the most perfect son you could
OL,21,Fever ask for."
