OL,6,FThey continued: "He was so easy going
OL,7,Fand laid back, a really positive guy.
OL,9,F"Loving, caring, fun and happy, he was
OL,10,Ffull of fun, character and life.
OL,12,F"Ben loved cars, car shows, and his
OL,13,Fcat and he was loved by all of his
OL,14,Ffriends and family."
OL,16,FSussex Police is asking for
OL,17,Finformation or dash cam footage from
OL,18,Fthe time of the collision.
